title: Tutorial
description: The perfect guide to an aspiring mercenary.

data.text:
Welcome my dear mercenary! It is I Mr. Deshapanesha, your local billionare, and before you dive into your assignment, I would like to offer you some assistance. You are going to be exploring a few huge labyrinths to find and kill the targets I've laid out for you. So I've prepared some things to boost your chances of success!.


Use WASD to move.

You will notice that you are holding a bag of crumbs, bread crumbs, to be specific. You will be able to lay down these crumbs whilst exploring the massive mazes in order to mark where've you been before.


Move your mouse to change the direction you're pointing in and left click to use your selected item (Bread crumbs).

Now! pick up the pistol I have so kindly provided to you. It isn't the most powerful weapon, however it should serve you well in fighting off the hoards monsters in the mazes. Speaking of which, I have gathered a few of those monsters for you to practice on! Go on now, kill the beasts and then pick up the phone on the other side of the arena!


When you have multiple items you can use the number keys shown on your HUD to switch between the item in your hand.
